@waltonseymour I have been using a simpler workaround described in this PR: #2815.

You can try it with the following configuration in your task if you want to continue using the Vanilla version of Druid:

```
    "tuningConfig" : {
      ...
      "jobProperties" : {
        "mapreduce.job.user.classpath.first": "true"
      },
      ...
    }
```

