@fjy hmmm...  looking at this after a while, this PR was last discussed to see if we could have json path as expression language for extracting information from nested avro records. I think it is ok to use the language already implemented in this PR and no suitable java impl for json path based avro extraction exists and also json path is designed for json data really. there is one in scala but I would prefer not to bring scala in the mix here as that introduces its own set of complications.
also, in future, we can change things if we really wanted while maintaining full backward compatibility.
